window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Max Troika never thought he’d be the alpha of his pack. That was his older brother’s fate. Assassinations have a way of ruining everything. Including who Max can take as a mate. It sure isn’t the cute and curvy librarian inspiring his dirtiest dream every night.</p> <p>Galyna Shirvan has it bad for a guy she never thought a chubby librarian like her could ever win over. Now he’s got all the hots for her, too.</p> <p>But there’s something strange about Max. No, it must be her imagination and all those paranormal romance novels the teens keep telling her to read.</p> <p>Werewolves aren’t real.</p> <p><i>Ahrooo....</i></p>"; 
